author: Ken Moritsugu | AP
title: Virus data: What's known and not known about China's numbers
description: Every few days brings another grim milestone in the coronavirus outbreak
content: There is no smoking gun pointing to a cover-up by Chinas ruling Communist Party. But intentional or not, there is reason to believe that more people died of COVID-19 than the official tally, which stood at 3,312 at the end of Tuesday. The same applies to the … [+7446 chars]
